With which HP APM persona should a salesperson discuss diagnosing application
performance issues before the application is released into production?
A. director of applications monitoring
B. director of operations
C. director of performance testing
D. director of mobile applications
Answer: C

integrated HP APM solution? (Select three.)
A. application discovery and dependency mapping
B. user experience monitoring
C. storage usage
D. transaction profiling
E. virtual tracking
F. service ticket automation
Answer: A,B,D
